job.title: CGCRI Project Assistant Recruitment 2021  Apply offline for 15  vacancies in Kolkata
job.body:
Total vacancies:15

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Project Associate-I
  • project Assistant
  • Junior Research Fellow
  • Project Scientist-I

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by CSIR-Central Glass and Ceramic Research Institute for the vacancies of Project Assistant If you are finding a government job in KOLKATA then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in KOLKATA, from 03.06.2021, and till 13.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in KOLKATA and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for CGCRI Project Assistant posts in KOLKATA:

  • To apply for a Project Assistant post in KOLKATA, your Diploma, Degree, B.Tech / B.E, ME/M.Tech must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 13.05.2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 03.06.2021.

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 50  years old. 

CGCR Project Assistant Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 56,000

How to apply for CGCRI Project Assistant Recruitment 2021

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly download the application form there and easily start the application process of these vacancies in KOLKATA. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of CGCRI and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY CGCRI
  • Print out the application form
  • Fill up the detailed ask in the application form by blue or black pen
  • Now send this application form to the address mentioned in the official notification

Download Official notification pdf
